font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Sorag we g&ouml;zleg</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Keseli&#328;
d&ouml;remegini&#328; tebigaty, serho&#351;lyk, dem aly&#351; ulgamyny&#328;
alamatlary, in&ccedil;ekesel, birle&#351;&yacute;&auml;n keseller bilen
n&auml;sagy&#328; aragatna&#351;ygyny&#328; bolmagy, immuniteti bas&yacute;an
islendik dermanlar bilen bejergini&#328; dowamlylygy barada hassany&#328;
i&ccedil;gin g&ouml;zlegleri ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r. in&ccedil;ekesele
gar&#351;y sanjym etmek bilen birlikde.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Synag wagtynda lukman hassany
umumy g&ouml;zden ge&ccedil;ir&yacute;&auml;r, bedeni&#328; gyzgynlygyny, gan
basy&#351;yny, &yacute;&uuml;rek urmasyny we dem al&#351;yny, derini&#328; we
g&ouml;r&uuml;n&yacute;&auml;n gyjyndyrmalary&#328; barlagyny, limfa d&uuml;w&uuml;nlerini&#328;
palpasi&yacute;asyny (barlagyny), auskultasi&yacute;a (di&#328;lemek)
&ouml;l&ccedil;&auml;r. &ouml;&yacute;ken we &yacute;&uuml;rek,
&#351;e&yacute;le hem serho&#351;lygy&#328;, &uuml;sg&uuml;lewigi&#328; we
demi&#328; agyrlygyna baha ber&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

