</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>T&uuml;berk&uuml;lin Anykla&yacute;y&#351;&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>immun
t&uuml;berk&uuml;lin (enjekte cilt &ouml;s&uuml;p netij&auml;
kesgitle&yacute;&auml;n ybarat&nbsp;<i>Mantoux gar&#351;ylyk&nbsp;</i>di&#328;e
Mycobacterium tuberculosis v&uuml;cudun bir jogap seb&auml;bi), &yacute;a-da
protein (&nbsp;<i>diaskintest&nbsp;</i>).&nbsp;In&ccedil;ekesel diagnostikasy
di&#328;e &ccedil;agalary&#328; we &yacute;etginjekleri&#328; hassalaryny&#328;
arasynda &ouml;z &auml;hmi&yacute;etini saklady.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>T-spot gan barlagy (T-SPOT)&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>we&nbsp;<b>kwantiferon
synagy&nbsp;</b>in&ccedil;ekesel bilen gizlin &yacute;okan&ccedil;lygy,
&#351;ol sanda ekstrapulmoner g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;leri we keseli&#328;
i&#351;je&#328; tapgyryny anyklamaga ukyplydyr.&nbsp;Der&#328;ew
&uuml;&ccedil;in alnan gan wirusly mikobakteri&yacute;a
in&ccedil;ekeselini&#328; bir b&ouml;legi bolan &yacute;&ouml;rite
sa&yacute;lanan antigen beloklary (ESAT6 we CFP10) bilen
gyjyndyryl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Bu gyjyndyrma jogap h&ouml;km&uuml;nde CD4 we CD8 T
lenfositler interferon gamma &ouml;nd&uuml;r&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Netij&auml;ni&#328;
esasynda &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykarylan T-lenfositleri&#328; (T-spot) we
gamma-interferony&#328; (kwantiferon synagy) alynmagy.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
