color:black'>Ferment bilen baglany&#351;ykly immunosorbent
barlagy&nbsp;(ELISA)&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:
"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>, mikobakteri&yacute;alary&#328;
antigenlerine gar&#351;y emele gel&yacute;&auml;n gan seri&yacute;asyndaky
antikorlary kesgitlem&auml;ge m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik
ber&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;In&ccedil;ekeseli&#328; ekstrapulmoner
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;leri bolan adamlarda usuly&#328; maglumat mazmuny gaty
&yacute;okary.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
