</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>In&ccedil;ekesel bilen kesell&auml;n n&auml;saglary&#328;
hemmesine&nbsp;<b>AIW &yacute;oka&#351;masy barlan&yacute;ar&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;AIW
infeksi&yacute;asy in&ccedil;ekeseli&#328; dolandyryly&#351;yny
&uuml;&yacute;tgedip biler we bejergisi in&ccedil;ekeseli&#328; has &ccedil;alt
&ccedil;&ouml;z&uuml;lmegine seb&auml;p bolup biler.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>In&ccedil;ekesel prosesini&#328; g&uuml;&yacute;&ccedil;lenmegi
wagtynda&nbsp;<b>kliniki gan barlagy&nbsp;</b>k&ouml;plen&ccedil;
gemoglobini&#328; we eritrositleri&#328; birneme azalmagyny, k&ouml;p sanly
ne&yacute;trofili&#328;, lenfositleri&#328; sanyny&#328; azalmagyny we ESR
tizlenmesini &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykar&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>In&ccedil;ekeselli n&auml;saglarda&nbsp;<b>biohimiki gan barlagy&nbsp;</b>,&nbsp;<i>albumini&#328;&nbsp;</i>mukdaryny&#328;
azalandygyny&nbsp;we&nbsp;<i>alfa-1 we alfa-2 globulinleri&#328;&nbsp;</i>derejesini&#328;
&yacute;okarlanandygyny g&ouml;rkez&yacute;&auml;r&nbsp;(&yacute;iti fazaly
beloklary&#328; sintezini&#328; &yacute;okarlanmagy seb&auml;pli).&nbsp;Gizlin
i&#351;je&#328; &ccedil;i&#351;me prosesinde&nbsp;<i>C-reaktiw belogy&nbsp;</i>kesgitlemek
m&ouml;h&uuml;mdir&nbsp;.&nbsp;S&uuml;&#328;kleri&#328; we bogunlary&#328;
in&ccedil;ekeselinde&nbsp;<i>a&#351;gar fosfatazy&#328;&nbsp;</i>i&#351;je&#328;ligini&#328;
ep-esli &yacute;okarlanmagy &yacute;&uuml;ze
&ccedil;yk&yacute;ar&nbsp;.&nbsp;B&ouml;wrek funksi&yacute;asyny&#328;
&yacute;aramazla&#351;magy kreatini&#328; k&ouml;pelmeginde, glomerul&yacute;ar
s&uuml;zg&uuml;&ccedil; tizligini&#328; &uuml;&yacute;tgemeginde
&yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykyp
biler.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
