</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Si&yacute;digi&#328; umumy seljermesini&#328;&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&uuml;&yacute;tgemegi&nbsp;b&ouml;wrekleri&#328;
we pe&#351;ew &yacute;ollaryny&#328; mikobakteri&yacute;a zeperlenmeleri bilen
&yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykar.&nbsp;Si&yacute;dikde iri&#328;, belok we
